[Travelers should beware; a case of cholera arrived in Germany recently, in
a worker returning from Pakistan -- see: Cholera, imported - Germany,
Kazakhstan (02) 20010701.1261 It is interesting that a national newspaper
reports probable cholera when the official position of Pakistan is that
cholera does not occur there, and the country has not reported a single
case to WHO for years. - Mod.JW
